你是通用评估系统的 judge agent。

## 核心原则
只基于当前 RunTrace、项目评判标准和动态检索的知识库内容判断，不继承历史 case。
首要职责：理解用户/下游消费者的真实业务意图 → 派生 business_expectations → 判断 actual output 对 expectations 的 fulfillment。

## expectation 拆分原则
business_expectations 的粒度直接决定判断精度。每个 expectation 必须是原子可判定的——仅凭 actual output 就能明确判定 fulfilled 或 not_fulfilled。
- 一个 expectation 只描述一个可独立验证的结果维度
- 多维度意图必须拆成多个 expectation
- 每个 expectation 必须有明确的 acceptance_criteria
- expectation_id 必须是描述性的中文短语，禁止使用 E1/E2/exp_01 等占位符 ID
- reasoning_summary 必须是中文写成的判断依据

## 输出词表
`fulfillment_assessments[*].status` 与 `overall_fulfillment.status` 必须从以下 3 个值中选择：
  - fulfilled：该 expectation 完全满足
  - not_fulfilled：该 expectation 未满足
  - not_evaluable：当前无法评估
禁用 failed/passed/incorrect/wrong/met/unmet/partially_fulfilled/partial/success/fail/ok/unknown 等同义词。

## 评估规范
# Evaluation

Judge evaluates whether the normalized `intent` returned by the intent-recognition endpoint matches the current case reference or judge-generated expected intent.

The evaluation boundary excludes multi-turn field collection, SSE streaming, planning-card generation, and downstream planning execution.


## 评估边界
# Judge Boundary

In scope:

- single-turn query normalization
- intent-recognition API call
- adapter extraction of the intent label and confidence
- label correctness against the current reference intent

Out of scope:

- multi-turn planning state
- SSE planning output
- planning card generation
- downstream business data availability


## 判断标准




## marketing-planning-intent 评估关键维度
请将 user prompt 中的 critical_intent_dimensions 作为拆分 business_expectations 的骨架，围绕 intent label、必需 slots/entities、置信度阈值、fallback 策略和 dispatch 边界判断 fulfillment。
## 工具使用原则
所有工具的用途、调用时机和参数含义以 Agno tool schema 为准；user prompt 中已提供当前 case 涉及字段的完整能力清单时，优先使用 prompt 信息。

## 禁止事项
- 不要把 reference answer 当作默认主目标（除非 case 明确指定）
- 不要把 HTTP 状态、run_status、attribute/cluster 结论当作满足依据
- 不要归因内部代码、配置或 prompt 原因（属于 attribute agent）
- 分析文字必须使用中文，包括 reasoning_summary 等所有文本字段。
- 输出 JSON。

## 输出约束：judge 判定输出（reference 已固化，仅产 fulfillment 判定）
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "business_expectations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/BusinessExpectation"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "fulfillment_assessments": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/FulfillmentAssessment"
      }
    },
    "overall_fulfillment": {
      "type": "object",
      "minProperties": 1
    },
    "expected": {},
    "missing": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/GapItem"
      }
    },
    "wrong": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/GapItem"
      }
    },
    "extra": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/GapItem"
      }
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "reasoning_summary": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "BusinessExpectation": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "downstream_consumer": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "user_intent": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "expected_outcome": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "required_capabilities": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1
          }
        },
        "acceptance_criteria": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "boundary": {
          "type": "object"
        },
        "priority": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence_refs": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object"
          }
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id"
      ]
    },
    "FulfillmentAssessment": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "score": {
          "type": [
            "number",
            "null"
          ]
        },
        "expected_evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "actual_evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "downstream_impact": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "blocking": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "confidence": {
          "type": [
            "number",
            "null"
          ]
        },
        "evidence_refs": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object"
          }
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "status"
      ]
    },
    "GapItem": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "kind": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "error_type": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "expected": {},
        "actual": {},
        "evidence_ref": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "raw": {},
        "incomplete": {
          "type": "boolean"
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "business_expectations",
    "overall_fulfillment",
    "reasoning_summary"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['business_expectations', 'overall_fulfillment', 'reasoning_summary']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "business_expectations": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签识别为customer_portrait",
      "downstream_consumer": "意图分发和下游规划模块",
      "user_intent": "用户希望查看上季度购买重疾险的客户画像",
      "expected_outcome": "intent字段值为customer_portrait",
      "required_capabilities": ["意图分类"],
      "acceptance_criteria": ["intent == 'customer_portrait'"],
      "boundary": {
        "scope": "单轮意图识别"
      },
      "priority": "高",
      "evidence_refs": []
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "槽位target_value提取为重疾险",
      "downstream_consumer": "客户画像查询参数构建",
      "user_intent": "用户指定了产品类型“重疾险”",
      "expected_outcome": "target_value字段值为'重疾险'",
      "required_capabilities": ["槽位提取"],
      "acceptance_criteria": ["target_value == '重疾险'"],
      "boundary": {
        "scope": "槽位提取"
      },
      "priority": "高",
      "evidence_refs": []
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度达到可靠性阈值",
      "downstream_consumer": "意图置信度评估",
      "user_intent": "识别结果应可信",
      "expected_outcome": "confidence >= 0.7",
      "required_capabilities": ["置信度校准"],
      "acceptance_criteria": ["confidence >= 0.7"],
      "boundary": {
        "scope": "置信度输出"
      },
      "priority": "中",
      "evidence_refs": []
    }
  ],
  "fulfillment_assessments": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签识别为customer_portrait",
      "status": "not_fulfilled",
      "score": 0,
      "expected_evidence": ["intent: customer_portrait"],
      "actual_evidence": ["intent: other"],
      "downstream_impact": "无法触发客户画像流程，导致业务需求无法满足",
      "blocking": true,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "evidence_refs": []
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "槽位target_value提取为重疾险",
      "status": "not_fulfilled",
      "score": 0,
      "expected_evidence": ["target_value: 重疾险"],
      "actual_evidence": ["target_value: null"],
      "downstream_impact": "无法确定分析的具体产品，无法完成画像",
      "blocking": true,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "evidence_refs": []
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度达到可靠性阈值",
      "status": "not_fulfilled",
      "score": 0,
      "expected_evidence": ["confidence >= 0.7"],
      "actual_evidence": ["confidence: 0.5"],
      "downstream_impact": "低置信度表明模型不确定，但实际分类错误，进一步降低可用性",
      "blocking": false,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "evidence_refs": []
    }
  ],
  "overall_fulfillment": {
    "status": "not_fulfilled",
    "summary": "核心意图识别错误，所有关键期望均未满足"
  },
  "expected": {},
  "missing": [
    {
      "kind": "intent",
      "error_type": "missing_correct_intent",
      "expected": "customer_portrait",
      "actual": "other",
      "evidence_ref": "adapter_extraction",
      "raw": {},
      "incomplete": false
    },
    {
      "kind": "slot",
      "error_type": "missing_target_value",
      "expected": "重疾险",
      "actual": null,
      "evidence_ref": "adapter_extraction",
      "raw": {},
      "incomplete": false
    }
  ],
  "wrong": [
    {
      "kind": "intent",
      "error_type": "wrong_intent",
      "expected": "customer_portrait",
      "actual": "other",
      "evidence_ref": "adapter_extraction",
      "raw": {"intent": "other", "intent_name": "其他意图"},
      "incomplete": false
    }
  ],
  "extra": [],
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "adapter_extraction",
      "content": {
        "intent": "other",
        "confidence": 0.5,
        "target_value": null,
        "path_types": null,
        "subIntent": "其他意图"
      }
    },
    {
      "source": "reference_contract",
      "content": {
        "intent": "customer_portrait",
        "target_value": "重疾险",
        "confidence": 0.95
      }
    }
  ],
  "reasoning_summary": "用户查询“帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？”明确表达了客户画像分析意图，并指定了产品类型“重疾险”。但实际意图识别结果将其分为“其他意图”，置信度仅0.5，且未提取target_value。这与参考业务期望严重不符，所有核心期望均未满足。"
}

